{"id": 2887, "genre": 1001, "title": "你见过/遭受过哪些披着“企业文化”外衣的职场欺凌？", "description": "我们讲究蚕性文化，到死丝方尽。", "record_count": 5156, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190408165126CXUJTtVBfk4v6r9s.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-04-09T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 338176, "content": "实习期3-6个月，你去死吧，你得多瞎要3个月才能看出一个人能不能在你们公司干活...", "image": null, "praise_count": 590, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 338432, "content": "出差的时候非要凌晨飞机，后半夜睡觉，一天工作22小时，之后不算加班，说没打卡记录。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297165}, {"id": 338178, "content": "必须随叫随到，“我们这个行业没有周末一说”…", "image": null, "praise_count": 310, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632471}, {"id": 338179, "content": "团建去死... 不如你给每个人加500工资 ，这样员工会更有凝聚力。", "image": null, "praise_count": 377, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972975}, {"id": 338180, "content": "不但打着公司文化，还传承者中国历史的文化来压迫你。陪客户的酒局，内部的人情世故。给工作带来很多的不便", "image": null, "praise_count": 138, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632483}, {"id": 338181, "content": "用责任感道德绑架强迫你加班。", "image": null, "praise_count": 79, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1406417}, {"id": 338184, "content": "恒房通", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869386}, {"id": 338185, "content": "刚进的新人被到处使唤", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619106}, {"id": 338186, "content": "每天早晨向传销一样喊好很好非常好", "image": null, "praise_count": 217, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323389}, {"id": 338187, "content": "团建", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224481}, {"id": 338189, "content": "我们科室的活加班也干不完🙂", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1604619}, {"id": 338190, "content": "目前对喜欢做的事加班多久也是愿意的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622114}, {"id": 338191, "content": "占用课余时间开党课……🌚", "image": null,